### List all messages
GET http://localhost:3000/messages

### Get message by id
GET http://localhost:3000/messages/727

### Post new message
POST http://localhost:3000/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": "once more, hello again dude!"
}

### Post new invalid message type
POST http://localhost:3000/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content": 42
}
